{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "vop", "tags": "rman,displayfilter", "icon": "NETWORKS/shop", "internal": "pxrlightsaturation", "version": "3.0", "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["pxrlightsaturation"], "extent": [74, 97]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["A small example display filter that changes the color saturation in the beauty pass (or any other AOV) according to whether a region is lit or shadowed by particular light group."], "extent": [97, 278]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [278, 290], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["AOV"], "extent": [290, 300], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 7, "text": ["Name of a color AOV to adjust saturation in."], "extent": [322, 375]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channel": "/aov"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Light AOV"], "extent": [375, 390], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 7, "text": ["Name of the color AOV with the contribution from the light group. The AOV should be populated using a direct-lighting LPE such as: ", {"tag": "p", "attrs": {}, "type": "xml", "text": [" Display '+satlighttiny' 'null' 'color lpe:C", {"scheme": null, "value": "DGS", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/DGS.html"}, "<L.'tiny'>' "]}, " in which case the value of this parameter would be 'satlighttiny'. This AOV shows direct illumination from any lights with parameter: ", {"tag": "p", "attrs": {}, "type": "xml", "text": [" 'string __group' 'tiny' "]}], "extent": [414, 789]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channel": "/light"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Threshold"], "extent": [789, 804], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 7, "text": ["Luminance in the light AOV less than this is considered shadowed."], "extent": [832, 906]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channel": "/threshold"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Invert?"], "extent": [906, 919], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 7, "text": ["If unset then areas lit by the light will be modified and areas fully in shadow will be left alone.  Set this to invert that and change the saturation of the shadows of this light."], "extent": [944, 1133]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channel": "/invert"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Shift"], "extent": [1133, 1144], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 7, "text": ["Amount and direction to shift saturation.  Positive values increase saturation, negative values desaturate.  Recommended range is -2.0 to 2.0."], "extent": [1168, 1319]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channel": "/shift"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Parameters"}], "title": ["pxrlightsaturation"]}